## **AUTK-PLOT: LINKED D3 CHARTS**

Entry point: Chart classes (`Barchart`, `Scatterplot`, `ParallelCoordinates`)

### **Common Configuration**

All chart types share `PlotConfig`:

```typescript
import { Barchart, Scatterplot, ParallelCoordinates } from 'autk-plot';

const chart = new Barchart({
  div: document.querySelector('#chart-container') as HTMLElement,
  data: geojson, // FeatureCollection — uses feature.properties as rows
  labels: {
    axis: ['neighborhood', 'population'], // [x-axis, y-axis]
    title: 'Population by Neighborhood',
  },
  width: 600,
  height: 400,
  margins: { left: 80, right: 20, top: 40, bottom: 60 }, // optional
});
```

### **Chart Types**

#### 1. **Bar Chart** (Categorical × Numeric)
```typescript
import { Barchart } from 'autk-plot';

const chart = new Barchart({
  div: document.querySelector('#chart') as HTMLElement,
  data: geojson,
  labels: {
    axis: ['neighborhood', 'population'], // [categorical, numeric]
    title: 'Population by Neighborhood',
  },
  width: 600,
  height: 400,
});

// Supports CLICK event
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.CLICK, (selectedIds) => {
  console.log('Clicked indices:', selectedIds);
});
```

#### 2. **Scatter Plot** (Numeric × Numeric)
```typescript
import { Scatterplot } from 'autk-plot';

const chart = new Scatterplot({
  div: document.querySelector('#chart') as HTMLElement,
  data: geojson,
  labels: {
    axis: ['area', 'height'], // [x numeric, y numeric]
    title: 'Building Area vs Height',
  },
  width: 600,
  height: 400,
});

// Supports BRUSH event (2D rectangular selection)
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH, (selectedIds) => {
  console.log('Brushed indices:', selectedIds);
});
```

#### 3. **Parallel Coordinates** (Multiple Numeric Axes)
```typescript
import { ParallelCoordinates } from 'autk-plot';

const chart = new ParallelCoordinates({
  div: document.querySelector('#chart') as HTMLElement,
  data: geojson,
  labels: {
    axis: ['area', 'height', 'floors', 'year_built'], // all numeric
    title: 'Building Attributes',
  },
  width: 800,
  height: 400,
});

// Supports BRUSH_X and BRUSH_Y events (per-axis brushing)
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH_X, (selectedIds) => {
  console.log('Filtered by X:', selectedIds);
});

chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH_Y, (selectedIds) => {
  console.log('Filtered by Y:', selectedIds);
});
```

### **Interactivity**

#### 1. **Plot Events**
```typescript
import { PlotEvent } from 'autk-plot';

// CLICK — on bar charts
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.CLICK, (selectedIds) => { ... });

// BRUSH — on scatter plots
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH, (selectedIds) => { ... });

// BRUSH_X, BRUSH_Y — on parallel coordinates
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH_X, (selectedIds) => { ... });
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH_Y, (selectedIds) => { ... });
```

`selectedIds` is array of row indices (by position in `data.features`).

#### 2. **Highlighting from Map**
```typescript
chart.setHighlightedIds(selectedIds);
```

### **Linked Views** (Bidirectional)

```typescript
import { MapEvent } from 'autk-map';
import { PlotEvent, Scatterplot } from 'autk-plot';

// Map → Chart
map.updateRenderInfoProperty('buildings', 'isPick', true);
map.mapEvents.on(MapEvent.PICK, (ids) => {
  chart.setHighlightedIds(ids);
});

// Chart → Map
chart.plotEvents.on(PlotEvent.BRUSH, (ids) => {
  chart.setHighlightedIds(ids); // keep chart in sync
  map.updateGeoJsonLayerThematic(
    'buildings',
    geojson,
    (_f, i) => ids.includes(i) ? 1.0 : 0.0
  );
});
```

